Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:15.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:18.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.36,0:00:25.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You came here to pick a fight with Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.32,0:00:27.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's suicidal!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.24,0:00:29.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fro thinks so, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.98,0:02:04.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.50,0:02:09.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anybody who doesn't think of \Ntheir comrades as comrades
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.32,0:02:11.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,is on my list!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.34,0:02:13.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he talking about Yukino?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.21,0:02:16.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's got nothin' to do with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.55,0:02:19.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would storm in here \Nover something like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.00,0:02:22.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're talking about,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.55,0:02:27.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but I suppose you've got your reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.65,0:02:30.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know what I'm talkin' about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.66,0:02:32.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobengal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.14,0:02:33.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Deal with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:34.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.45,0:02:36.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're avoiding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:41.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A guild soldier like you needs \N100 more years of experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:47.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want a shot at the top, you'll have \Nto prove yourself. Show me what you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.20,0:02:52.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pandemonium!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:56.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.08,0:02:58.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting near the master!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.76,0:03:10.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Dobengal, am not taking \Npart in the Grand Magic Games,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.84,0:03:15.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but when it comes to skill, I'm just as \Nstrong as any of the participants here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:18.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to show you \Nthe power of Sabertooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:23.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A smokescreen, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.89,0:03:29.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know who you're messing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:31.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should withdraw immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:32.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:34.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.35,0:03:37.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My beef ain't with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.52,0:03:41.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.64,0:03:42.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobengal's down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.60,0:03:47.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's one of the top ten strongest \Nwizards in our guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.47,0:03:51.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, let me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:53.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:57.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid, there aren't any like you in my guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.58,0:03:59.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.49,0:04:07.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:09.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...you've got?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:38.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Firing Hammer...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.43,0:04:41.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...of the Lightning Flame Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:01.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Minerva!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:03.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.00,0:05:13.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we end this evening's \Nentertainment here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:18.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Minerva, I didn't ask you to step in...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:20.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.01,0:05:24.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,if this had continued, you \Nwould have won, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.50,0:05:26.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.37,0:05:30.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the world cares about appearances.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.29,0:05:34.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though this one came \Nhere and attacked you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:40.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,if the master of Sabertooth annihilated \Na participant in the Grand Magic Games,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:43.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,it would cause difficulty for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.85,0:05:47.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell ya one thing... if anybody's \Ngettin' wiped out, it's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.65,0:05:50.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My father has somewhat warmed to this battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.08,0:05:54.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but cannot back down in \Nfront of his subordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.36,0:05:55.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:59.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you allow us to save face?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.15,0:06:08.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, I'll return this \Nkitten to you unharmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:11.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.69,0:06:15.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.65,0:06:17.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.55,0:06:20.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've incapacitated several of our people,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:24.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but we're willing to overlook this incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:29.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange, I'm asking you \Nto behave in a mature fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:39.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:43.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! They caught me at the entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.22,0:06:44.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, Happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:47.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault for leaving you behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:50.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.45,0:06:52.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.35,0:06:53.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.26,0:06:59.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That kid's got grit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:02.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll settle this at the Grand Magic Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:04.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To our hearts' content.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:09.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We ain't gonna lose to the likes of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:12.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, you won't be \Nable to keep up with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:21.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you call yourself a guild, \Ntake care of your comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:24.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.60,0:07:31.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Comrades...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.74,0:07:35.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have that kind of bond in our guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:40.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're that strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.61,0:07:42.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu Dragneel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:45.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I'm gonna compete tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:49.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just let him get \Naway with this carnage!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.08,0:07:52.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you're going to unleash the \Npower of Black Lightning, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.09,0:07:55.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly, this was rather one-sided carnage,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.05,0:08:01.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but without something like this, \Nwe would've lost our spark.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.55,0:08:04.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we need someone to replace Yukino.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:07.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll get in on the fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:14.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You fought Sabertooth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.78,0:08:17.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I wanted to mix \Nit up with 'em even more...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.63,0:08:20.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad it ended right as \NI was gettin' fired up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:22.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.82,0:08:25.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault, for getting caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:29.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?! We're \Nlucky it ended the way it did!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.14,0:08:30.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:33.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If one of their team \Nmembers had been injured,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:36.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,we might've been disqualified!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:41.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, that Minerva \Nchick was sayin' something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:44.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You{\i0} are incredibly stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:46.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Use your head a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.23,0:08:47.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:50.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pour it on, Gray! Read him the riot act!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.95,0:08:54.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were gonna take the fight \Nto them, you should've invited me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:58.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fair, you getting \Nto have all the fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.84,0:09:00.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're missing the point!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.99,0:09:03.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because you're frustrated \Nfrom losing a match,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:06.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,there's nothing admirable about getting \Npayback in a fight outside the arena.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.94,0:09:09.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what it's about!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.21,0:09:13.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to deliver a \Nmessage to that Rufus bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:15.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm not gonna lose next time!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.08,0:09:18.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm not lettin' \Nthose jerks off the hook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:22.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A comrade's someone who's got \Nyour back and you got theirs...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.36,0:09:25.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Being strict is one thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.94,0:09:30.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but humiliating a girl and then kicking \Nher out, that's as low as you can go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:33.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That Yukino girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,0:09:37.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,even after being abused like \Nthat, she came to see me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.20,0:09:40.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where she is now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.88,0:09:42.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:45.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She did say she has nowhere to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:50.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! I'm still seething!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:52.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll go back there \Nan' fight some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:54.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Count me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:56.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.23,0:09:59.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you just settle it at the tournament?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,0:10:02.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although now that you've riled up Sabertooth,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.50,0:10:06.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,from tomorrow on, they'll probably \Ngo even harder on us in the matches!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:12.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter which guild they're in,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.85,0:10:16.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,all wizards have their own feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.58,0:10:27.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:28.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:30.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:33.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.19,0:10:42.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you cut it out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:44.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.14,0:10:53.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.54,0:10:54.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,About last night, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.95,0:10:55.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:11:00.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, somebody \Nattacked Sabertooth's inn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.94,0:11:05.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of fool would \Npick a fight with Saber?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:07.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:10.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, brawls happen outside \Nthe arena every year, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:13.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a festival, so they \Nshould take it public!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.04,0:11:18.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu-sama...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:26.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A guild that makes its family \Nmembers cry ain't no guild at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:31.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he did it for...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:42.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're at the halfway point \Nin the Grand Magic Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:44.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The beginning of the third day!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:48.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what kind of passionate \Ndramas we'll see today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.80,0:11:50.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our guest today
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:54.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,is Lahar-san, from the Magic Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.55,0:11:56.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:58.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for this opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:12:03.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lahar-san, you're the Captain of the \NEnforcement and Detention Corps...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.52,0:12:04.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.86,0:12:08.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't stand for any shenanigans \Nduring the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:12.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the captain for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:15.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He never forgets his duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.34,0:12:17.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Lahar...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.14,0:12:19.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you make me come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.81,0:12:26.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A guest of the Grand Magic Games?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.61,0:12:27.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:30.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no reason to decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.73,0:12:32.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me, Doranbolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:34.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.61,0:12:38.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to see Fairy Tail \Nalive and well, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:40.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you wonder about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:43.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:45.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, the way I am now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:49.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still hung up on what \Nhappened seven years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.57,0:12:52.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,About what you perceive of \Nas abandoning Fairy Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:57.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're looking forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:13:01.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The only one who's dragged \Ndown by the past is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:10.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! The match is starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.62,0:13:13.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault! You just had to get \Na fish-kebab from that food stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.74,0:13:16.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It smelled so good, I couldn't help myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.74,0:13:18.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, let's just hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.76,0:13:24.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to announce the competition \Nfor this, the third day of the Games!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:26.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The name of the event...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.75,0:13:28.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...is Pandemonium!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:31.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What does "pandemonium" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:33.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an abode of demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:37.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a building where lots of demons lurk...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:40.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they're doing a haunted house...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.66,0:13:43.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're walking down a \Ndark path and suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:47.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...something like this jumps out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.24,0:13:50.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I like "pandemonium"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.82,0:13:53.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm scared, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:56.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you're a ghost yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.32,0:14:00.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There will be one participant \Nfrom each guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:02.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please choose your representative!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:04.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.45,0:14:07.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta continue what I started last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.29,0:14:09.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get to decide all by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.60,0:14:13.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's a revenge match, I wanna do it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.19,0:14:16.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:20.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You going out there may only \Nmake things more complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.43,0:14:23.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree! Good luck, Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:24.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.85,0:14:26.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:29.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you calm down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:31.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll participate for B Team.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:33.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.16,0:14:35.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time that I get to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:39.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cana, how could you go, when \Nyou're a reserve member?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.17,0:14:41.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Mystogan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:43.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia hasn't seen him yet today...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:46.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With the guest commentator \Nbeing a member of the Council,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:48.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I should be able to participate, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.60,0:14:50.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.11,0:14:54.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If Er-chan is gonna do this, \Nlet me go too, Kagura-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.77,0:14:56.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.38,0:15:00.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna lose, Er-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.24,0:15:01.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.86,0:15:04.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate Jellal, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.85,0:15:06.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He used us...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:09.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...and murdered Simon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:10.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forgive him...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.56,0:15:12.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forgive him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,0:15:18.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to focus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:21.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From Mermaid Heel, it looks like \NMillianna is taking the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:23.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.58,0:15:24.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Millianna...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.85,0:15:28.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the one who was wearing the hood. \NI didn't know she was in a guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.95,0:15:34.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cause trouble in \Nfront of the Council, Obra.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.76,0:15:38.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the rep for Pegasus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.45,0:15:42.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said last night, I'm \Nparticipating in this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.14,0:15:45.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use my Black Lightning to \Nblast them all to smithereens.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.85,0:15:49.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we don't know what kind \Nof competition it's going to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:53.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.58,0:15:57.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If Natsu Dragneel isn't gonna be \Nin it, I don't care what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:02.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jura-san is going to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.17,0:16:04.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On Obaba's orders, so we \Ncan't do anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.84,0:16:06.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My sock...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:07.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just buy a new one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:10.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.34,0:16:13.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All of the participants have been selected!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:15.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From Sabertooth, Orga!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:17.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From Lamia Scale, Jura!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:19.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From Blue Pegasus, Hibiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.63,0:16:21.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From Raven Tail, Obra!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:24.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From Mermaid Heel, Millianna!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:26.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From Quatro Puppy, Novali!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.44,0:16:28.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From Fairy Tail A, Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:30.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From Fairy Tail B, Cana!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:33.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,These are our eight competitors!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:50.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.20,0:16:51.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.83,0:16:58.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin analysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:14.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pandemonium, a temple \Nhaunted by evil monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:16.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.81,0:17:20.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Haunted by monsters, he says?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.05,0:17:22.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the idea-kabo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:27.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are 100 monsters inside this temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:30.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That being said, they're actually \Nmagical manifestations that we created,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.93,0:17:34.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so everyone can relax. There's \Nno danger of you being attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:38.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The monsters are D, C, B, A, S!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:41.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the five levels of battle \Npower the monsters are divided into.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.65,0:17:44.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how it breaks down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:46.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.13,0:17:50.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...if you're curious about just how \Nstrong the D-class monsters are...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.29,0:18:09.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ones like these
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.43,0:18:12.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and ones even stronger, 100 of them \Nwandering around the temple...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.96,0:18:15.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Pandemonium-kabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.51,0:18:20.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he says they're \Njust magical manifestations,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.11,0:18:22.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,if you get attacked by them, \Nyou're hurt for real, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.93,0:18:25.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Erza and Cana be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.56,0:18:28.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to think that those \Ntwo will be alright, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.19,0:18:31.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a really extravagant \Ncompetition, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.68,0:18:34.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it feels like they may \Nbe going a little too far...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.17,0:18:41.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please note that as the class \Nof the monsters goes up,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.08,0:18:44.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,their fighting strength \Nincreases exponentially.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.28,0:18:47.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The S-class monster is so strong \Nthat there's no guarantee
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.40,0:18:51.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,even one of the 10 Great Wizard \NSaints can defeat it-kabo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.31,0:18:58.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In order, each of you will choose \Nthe number of monsters to battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.52,0:19:01.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called your "right to challenge".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.05,0:19:02.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right to challenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.85,0:19:05.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, if you choose three monsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.69,0:19:09.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,three of them will appear inside the temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:12.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The person who chooses them \Nenters the temple alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:18.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If the player successfully destroys \Nthem, he or she gets three points.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.95,0:19:24.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The next player then has the right to \Nchallenge up to 97 of the remaining monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:27.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And so on and so on,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.65,0:19:30.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,until there are zero monsters left!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.11,0:19:35.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alternatively, if everyone runs out of magic \Npower, the game is over at that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.81,0:19:37.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a counting game.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:39.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.39,0:19:43.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Assessing the situation when your \Nturn comes around becomes important!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.29,0:19:45.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However, as I mentioned before,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:48.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the monsters are ranked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.85,0:19:52.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether the player uses their \Nright to challenge one or five,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.16,0:19:55.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the monsters appear randomly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:20:02.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you need a strategy to avoid \Nrunning into the S-class monster, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.75,0:20:07.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's random, having a strategy \Nlike that won't do you any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.40,0:20:12.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not true. Between probability \Ntheory and my Archive,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.92,0:20:15.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,strategy will work to some extent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.44,0:20:18.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Irrespective of the monster's rank,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.32,0:20:22.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll get one point for \Neach monster you destroy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.14,0:20:27.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you enter the temple, you \Ncan't exit until you've succeeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:31.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happens if we go down \Nwhile inside the temple?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.65,0:20:35.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The number of points you've earned \Nduring your turn stays as is,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.66,0:20:40.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but the number of destroys you've had \Nthat turn goes to zero, and you're out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.19,0:20:44.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's bad to get too greedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:49.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you only go with one monster per \Nturn, you'll fall behind the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.32,0:20:54.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you also have to consider how much magic \Nyou'll recover before it's your next turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:56.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is surprisingly difficult, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:21:00.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's see what happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.47,0:21:02.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...with the two from our guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:06.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's decide on the order.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.06,0:21:07.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please draw your lots.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:12.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Number one!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.40,0:21:18.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky! It'll go back around \Nto being your turn the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.15,0:21:20.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I got number eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.57,0:21:23.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With this competition,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.26,0:21:26.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought winning or losing all \Ndepended on the luck of the draw...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.29,0:21:30.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Luck of the draw? I don't know about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.58,0:21:32.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,More than the order of battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:36.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,pacing yourself and situational \Njudgment are important in this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.38,0:21:37.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.72,0:21:40.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a game anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.72,0:21:51.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All 100 will be my opponents!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.96,0:21:53.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I exercise my right to challenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.89,0:21:56.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...100!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.69,0:23:58.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,100 monsters all by herself, \Nshe says! Erza really is scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.91,0:24:01.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like Erza is the one who's the monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.81,0:24:03.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Does she actually have all that armor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.54,0:24:06.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven's Wheel Armor, Black Wing, \NFlame Empress, Sea Empress,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.42,0:24:08.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Flight, Adamantine, Giant, \NLightning Empress...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.86,0:24:12.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet she has, like, Red Ogre \NArmor and Hag Armor, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.17,0:24:14.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's gonna get mad at you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.21,0:24:16.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: 100 to 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.55,0:24:20.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But really, this is supposed to \Nbe a team competition, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.25,0:24:21.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, this is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.72,0:24:22.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it's Erza!
